    ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id], [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY

    WHEN [x.Bill.BillDetails].[SizeId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [dto.Size].[Name] AS [Name2]
FROM [BillDetails] AS [x.Bill.BillDetails]
INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [dto.Size] ON [x.Bill.BillDetails].[SizeId] = [dto.Size].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [dto.Color] ON [x.Bill.BillDetails].[ColorId] = [dto.Color].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [dto.Product] ON [x.Bill.BillDetails].[ProductId] = [dto.Product].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [dto.Product.ProductCategory] ON [dto.Product].[CategoryId] = [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]

    SELECT [x0].[Id], [x.Bill0].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [x0]
    INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [x.Size0] ON [x0].[SizeId] = [x.Size0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [x.Color0] ON [x0].[ColorId] = [x.Color0].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [x.Bill0] ON [x0].[BillId] = [x.Bill0].[Id]
    WHERE [x0].[BillId] = @__billId_0
) AS [t] ON [x.Bill.BillDetails].[BillId] = [t].[Id0]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [x.Bill.BillDetails].[Id], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
